sp_scores.title: Defeat the Spherimorph without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: The Spherimorph uses Elemental Shift to change its elemental weakness and resistance, kupo! After the shift, it counterattacks with the opposite element of its new weakness! Fire and ice are opposites, and so are lightning and water, kupo. The Spherimorph only counterattacks when you hit it with the element it's resistant to, so attack with care!
tip_battle.title: Spherimorph

sp_scores.title: Exploit the Crawler's weakness to lightning attacks.

tip_battle.message: When the Negator's on the battlefield, you can't use magic abilities or Soul Breaks, kupo! Take down the Negator first so you can use magic again, then attack the Crawler with its weakness, lightning!
tip_battle.title: Crawler & Negator

dungeon.epilogue: After they fought off the fiend in the spring, the party discovered a sphere left by Jecht in the water. Hearing from Auron that Jecht had sworn to battle Sin to the last, Tidus reaffirmed his dedication to their journey. After Yuna left for the temple with Seymour's butler, Trommel, the party was surrounded by Al Bhed. When Wakka learned that one of their attackers was Rikku's brother, a rift formed in the party's ranks, and Wakka headed off toward the temple alone.
dungeon.name: Macalania Woods
dungeon.prologue: On their way to Macalania Temple, Auron stops the party in Macalania Woods, taking them to a spring in the middle of the magical forest.
